cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is about statistical machine translation (SMT) between related languages using Byte Pair Encoding (BPE) and comparing it with other basic units. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of different basic units, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
